@NODE Installation
In order to install AppDecrunch you just drag the AppDecrunch icon to
whichever drawer you want to keep it in. In order for AppDecrunch to work
you must have some libraries installed, see Installation for details of
which libraries you need. You can install the libraries which I have
supplied by double clicking on the InstallLibs icon which I have provided.
@ENDNODE

@NODE Future
Possible future additions to AppDecrunch
========================================
